Chess.com (2020), 11th Hainan Danzhou Super-GM Tournament
English, Neo-Catalan declined (A14)

PGN here https://chess24.com/en/watch/live-tournaments/danzhou-2020/6/1/3

The 11th Hainan Danzhou Super-GM Tournament is an 8-player double round-robin that this year is taking place online on Chess.com due to the pandemic.

The time control is 15 minutes for all moves, with a 10-second increment from move 1.
